attributes.text: Turn left to stay on Thompson Dr

Bear right to Centreport Canada Way (MB-190)
At the traffic light, continue forward on Inkster Blvd (MB-190)
Turn left on McPhillips St (City Rte-180)
Keep left at the fork onto McPhillips St (City Rte-180)
